            "title": "What is your return & exchange policy?",
            "answer": "<p>At Prowl, we want you to love your purchase. If for any reason you need to return or exchange an item, here’s how it works:</p><p><strong>1. Eligibility</strong></p><ul><li>Items must be unworn, unwashed, unaltered, and with original tags attached.</li><li>Items with makeup, odors, deodorant, stains, or hair are considered damaged and cannot be accepted.</li><li>Returns must be initiated <strong>within 30 days</strong> of your order date.</li></ul><p><strong>2. How to Request a Return or Exchange</strong></p><ul><li>Email us at hello@prowloutdoors.com to request a return or exchange.</li><li>We will provide a return shipping label within 72 hours.</li></ul><p><strong>3. Shipping Costs</strong></p><ul><li>US exchanges are free.</li><li>US returns are currently free.</li><li>Original shipping costs are non-refundable.</li></ul><p><strong>4. Processing Returns</strong></p><ul><li>Once your return is received and inspected, we will email you to confirm receipt.</li><li>Approved refunds will be issued to your original payment method.</li><li>Refunds may take up to 10 business days to appear on your account, depending on your payment provider.</li></ul><p><strong>5. Non-Eligible Returns</strong></p><ul><li>Items that do not meet our policy will be returned to you.</li><li>We reserve the right to refuse returns showing signs of wear or damage.</li></ul>"
